Revision history for Test-HTML-Tidy-Recursive

0.6.2       2020-10-20
    - dist.ini / weaver.ini / .tidyallrc / etc. cleanup
        - Move to @SHLOMIF
        - Inspired by Lady_Aleena.

0.6.1       2019-05-17
    - Add "use strict" (Kwalitee).

0.6.0       2019-03-14
    - Convert from HTML::Tidy to HTML::T5.
        - HTML::Tidy is hard to install.

0.4.0       2017-11-30
    - Add the ::Strict subclass module.

0.2.1       2017-11-04
    - Update the $VERSION inside the .pm file.

0.2.0       2017-11-04
    - Extract and document the methods: traverse, check_file, check_using_tidy,
    and report_error - useful in subclassing.
    - Convert dist.ini to the @SHLOMIF PluginBundle.

v0.0.3      2017-02-27
    - Add a call to clear_messages() to avoid accumulating messages.
        - A non-security bug.

v0.0.2      2016-02-15
    - Fix the repository URLs to point to GitHub.
    - Add DESCRIPTION and SEE ALSO sections to the POD.

v0.0.1      2016-02-15
    - First version, released on an unsuspecting world

